parameters.name: KeyFilter
parameters.description: The tag key for a fuzzy query.

parameters.name: MaxResults
parameters.description:
The maximum number of entries to return for a single request.

Valid values: 1 to 100. Default value: 10.

parameters.name: NextToken
parameters.description: The pagination token that is used in the next request to retrieve a new page of results. You do not need to specify this parameter for the first request.

parameters.name: ResourceType
parameters.description:
The resource type.

The value Account indicates the members of the resource directory.
